            <p>Philad<hi rend="sup">a</hi> August the 8<hi rend="sup">th</hi>&#47;87.<lb/></p>
            <p>Rev. Dr. S. Morais&#44;<lb/> City<lb/>
                Reverend and dear Sir&#58;<lb/></p>
            <p>Some<lb/> two weeks ago&#44; when last you<lb/> favored me with a call&#44; you<lb/> informed me of the fact that<lb/> there is being circulated an<lb/> essay on religious subjects&#44; alle&#45;<lb/>ged to have been written by me.<lb/>  Not having seen it myself&#44; I<lb/> cannot say whether or not such<lb/> is the case&#44; but assuming that<lb/> it is the one which I wrote<lb/> on that subject more than two<lb/> years ago&#44; I desire it to be<lb/> distinctly understood that I never&#44;<lb/> either by direct approval or im&#45;<lb/></p>
                
                <pb n="2"/>
            <p>plication&#44; or in any other way<lb/> authorized anybody to publish&#44;<lb/> or in any other way circulate&#44;<lb/> the said essay&#44; and that it is<lb/> only by committing an un&#45;<lb/>pardonable breach of confidence<lb/> that it was possible to do it.<lb/></p>
            <p>I therefore beg<lb/> of you to protest in my name<lb/> against the circulation of the<lb/> essay in question&#44; and to deny<lb/> authoritatively that I entertain<lb/> at this moment any of the<lb/> sentiments expressed in it&#44; any<lb/> and all essays or assertions of<lb/> others to the contrary notwithstanding.<lb/></p>
            <p>Circumstances &#40;of a<lb/> private character&#44; and well known<lb/> to you&#41; prevent me from person&#45;<lb/>ally denying it publicly at the<lb/> present time&#44; &#40;though I shall surely<lb/> do so as soon as able&#41;&#44; and<lb/></p>
                <pb n="3"/>
            <p>therefore apply to you to do it<lb/> for me&#44; giving you full authority<lb/> in the matter.<lb/> I am&#44; dear Sir&#44; your<lb/> obedient servant<lb/> Gas<hi rend="sup">r</hi> Loewenthal<lb/></p>
                
            <p>N. B. You are at liberty to use<lb/> this in any way you may see<lb/> fit.<lb/> G. L.<lb/></p>
            </body>
    </text>
